  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Legal Consultant – Commercial",
  "description": "<p>Flexible Services from Pinsent Masons Vario provides legal professionals access to high-quality legal work with top-tier clients.<br />Our growing hub of legal experts have a variety of skills, specialisms and experience but they all enjoy quality legal projects best suited to their skillset and unparalleled support during their assignments.We are now looking to expand our bench with an exceptional commercial experience in hospitality sector.</p><p>To join our hub, you need to demonstrate the following:</p><ul><li>Qualified lawyer with a strong academic background</li><li>Top international law firm or equivalent in-house/secondment experience</li><li>Flexible, communicative and adaptable</li><li>Enthusiastic about embracing new work cultures</li><li>Rapidly develop close, trusting relationships</li></ul><p>As a legal consultant, you also need to possess:</p><ul><li>Minimum 5 years PQE in-house or within a law firm</li><li>Experience in commercial hospitality related agreements such as loyalty agreements, franchise agreements</li><li>Experience in dealing with stakeholders at different levels</li><li>Confidence to drop into a new team and hit the ground running</li></ul><p>To Apply, click on “Apply” and attach your latest CV. Alternatively, you can contact our Account Executive, Jasmine Liu at Jasmine.liu@pinsentmasons.com for a confidential conversation.</p>",
